# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using burner entities without fuel
- Ensure that the burner entities have sufficient fuel before using them.
### Errors when using inserter entities without source items
- Ensure that the inserter entities have source items to pick up before using them.
### Errors when using entities without ingredients
- Ensure that the entities have the required ingredients before using them.
### Errors when using steam engines without connection
- Ensure that the steam engines are connected to the boiler and the electricity network before using them.
### Errors when using pipe groups without fluid
- Ensure that the pipe groups have fluid to transport before using them.
### Errors when using belt groups without items
- Ensure that the belt groups have items to transport before using them.
### Errors when using electricity groups without connection to electric network
- Ensure that the electricity groups are connected to the electric network before using them.
